cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "SBGN Pathway Visualizer"
abstract: >-
  A standalone, browser-based tool to overlay RNA-seq and other omics data onto
  SBGN (Reactome) and KEGG (KGML) pathway maps. Rendering is deterministic and
  requires no API key or AI service.
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: Barker
    given-names: Richard
